{"TopicId":142020,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"Z-fighting shadows","CreatedByName":"Majorjim!","CreatedById":61954,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-18T14:53:42Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Majorjim!","CreatedById":61954,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-18T14:53:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi all,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0It is knows that the move to Unity 5 has caused a bug with the shadows. It is a kind of striping bug that is very noticeable and ugly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes anyone know if this is being looked at or if a fix is even possible because I have heard little from the devs on it. And I know it is a minor bug but it would be nice to know its going to be addressed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for reading and let me know here if you hear anything about this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Mechjeb (mod)\u0022\u003EMJ\u003C/abbr\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003EUPDATE: Here is the state of shadows in KSP unity 5.\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/SdDoqHZmY_8?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-06-21T18:34:33Z\u0022 title=\u002206/21/2016 06:34  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJune 21, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Majorjim\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AbacusWizard","CreatedById":116476,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-19T08:07:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes it look anything like this?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-XVCypXsXcOE/Ve0o2Cnh7eI/AAAAAAAABio/vch16FEchv4tCay1zOUPeQKLKV0jgFRPQCCo/s400/TankerShade1.png\u0022 alt=\u0022TankerShade1.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s a problem I saw frequently in an older version (0.90, probably?) and couldn\u0027t figure out why. It seemed to be completely fixed in 1.0.x; I haven\u0027t seen it in 1.1.x yet, but I haven\u0027t played 1.1.x much yet either.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"nosirrbro","CreatedById":69814,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-19T17:28:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you have scatterer?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Majorjim!","CreatedById":61954,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-19T20:45:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222636989\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142020\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466323678\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022116476\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AbacusWizard\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, AbacusWizard said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes it look anything like this?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo nothing like that mate.. If you load in a craft and look at the shadows, max settings, you will see a kind of rippling effect as the sun moves. It is very noticeable, and others have confirmed it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222637397\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142020\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466357297\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002269814\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022nosirrbro\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, nosirrbro said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you have scatterer?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo, no visual mods of any kind. only editor mods. It is present on a fully stock install too. I think either it is GPU/driver related or everyone has this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"He_162","CreatedById":152811,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-19T20:50:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222637601\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142020\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466369157\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002261954\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Majorjim\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, Majorjim said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo nothing like that mate.. If you load in a craft and look at the shadows, max settings, you will see a kind of rippling effect as the sun moves. It is very noticeable, and others have confirmed it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo, no visual mods of any kind. only editor mods. It is present on a fully stock install too. I think either it is GPU/driver related or everyone has this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can do some tests to see if it is driver related, because I have multiple computers, with different drivers settings, etc.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan you send screenshots of what to look for?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Majorjim!","CreatedById":61954,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-19T20:51:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222637610\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142020\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466369457\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022He_162\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, He_162 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can do some tests to see if it is driver related, because I have multiple computers, with different drivers settings, etc.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan you send screenshots of what to look for?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was looking for the one I posted a while back but cannot find it. I will post one tomorrow if possible mate.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"He_162","CreatedById":152811,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-19T20:52:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222637613\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142020\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466369512\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002261954\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Majorjim\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Majorjim said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was looking for the one I posted a while back but cannot find it. I will post one tomorrow if possible mate.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think I found what you were seeing... hold on\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Galileo","CreatedById":150430,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-19T20:53:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222637610\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142020\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466369457\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022He_162\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, He_162 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can do some tests to see if it is driver related, because I have multiple computers, with different drivers settings, etc.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan you send screenshots of what to look for?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s not really something you can see in a screenshot. I too have noticed the strange flag like waving of the shadows.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"He_162","CreatedById":152811,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-19T20:55:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere is a GIF showing the rippling in slower motion, just like 7 screenshots, but it shows that it happens.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/oKhoXIY\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://imgur.com/oKhoXIY\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNevermind.. the subtleness of it in this Install doesn\u0027t show in such low resolution.. hmm\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll see \u00A0if I can replicate it in a less subtle way to get it to show, and in a stock install with some simple editor mods.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-06-19T20:56:38Z\u0022 title=\u002206/19/2016 08:56  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJune 19, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by He_162\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Galileo","CreatedById":150430,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-19T21:21:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222637621\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142020\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466369722\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022He_162\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n25 minutes ago, He_162 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere is a GIF showing the rippling in slower motion, just like 7 screenshots, but it shows that it happens.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/oKhoXIY\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://imgur.com/oKhoXIY\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNevermind.. the subtleness of it in this Install doesn\u0027t show in such low resolution.. hmm\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll see \u00A0if I can replicate it in a less subtle way to get it to show, and in a stock install with some simple editor mods.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s really noticeable on the Kerbals themselves. \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"He_162","CreatedById":152811,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-19T21:25:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs it visible in this GIF?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/vp6cH1h\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://imgur.com/vp6cH1h\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Majorjim!","CreatedById":61954,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-19T21:28:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222637658\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142020\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466371531\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022He_162\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, He_162 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs it visible in this GIF?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/vp6cH1h\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://imgur.com/vp6cH1h\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKinda, in the cockpit. I will upload a video tomorrow if possible and show how noticeable it is.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"He_162","CreatedById":152811,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-19T21:46:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222637664\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142020\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466371701\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002261954\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Majorjim\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 minutes ago, Majorjim said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKinda, in the cockpit. I will upload a video tomorrow if possible and show how noticeable it is.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI found it was very random, and only happens in weird conditions, so it\u0027s hard to see what is going on.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Majorjim!","CreatedById":61954,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-19T21:53:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222637680\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142020\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466372793\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022He_162\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, He_162 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI found it was very random, and only happens in weird conditions, so it\u0027s hard to see what is going on.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLook at a kerbals face you will see it. Or line up some Ibeams on a wing surface and you will see it too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-06-19T21:53:32Z\u0022 title=\u002206/19/2016 09:53  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJune 19, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Majorjim\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"nosirrbro","CreatedById":69814,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-19T22:36:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222637690\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142020\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466373199\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002261954\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Majorjim\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n42 minutes ago, Majorjim said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLook at a kerbals face you will see it. Or line up some Ibeams on a wing surface and you will see it too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOhhh yeah I think I know what you mean, I\u0027ll try to get a screenshot if I can\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"He_162","CreatedById":152811,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-19T22:53:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222637754\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142020\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466375812\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002269814\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022nosirrbro\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 minutes ago, nosirrbro said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOhhh yeah I think I know what you mean, I\u0027ll try to get a screenshot if I can\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can see it in the cockpit of my second GIF image.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Corona688","CreatedById":2511,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-19T23:08:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222637601\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142020\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466369157\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002261954\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Majorjim\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Majorjim said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo nothing like that mate.. If you load in a craft and look at the shadows, max settings, you will see a kind of rippling effect as the sun moves.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEh, I\u0027ve noticed that in every game which has shadows for as long as I\u0027ve known to look for it.\u00A0 Unless you pump shadows up to a ludicrously high res, I don\u0027t think it\u0027s really avoidable.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"swjr-swis","CreatedById":152460,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-20T02:00:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTwo short videos showing the problem:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/kh0xp78mx2qnldk/KSP-ShadowWalking2.mp4?dl=0\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.dropbox.com/s/kh0xp78mx2qnldk/KSP-ShadowWalking2.mp4?dl=0\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/12x4r5iakwjfb5e/KSP-ShadowWalking3.mp4?dl=0\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.dropbox.com/s/12x4r5iakwjfb5e/KSP-ShadowWalking3.mp4?dl=0\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is with all graphics dials turned up to max, including shadows and lights, on a completely immobile scene.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheSaint","CreatedById":70033,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-20T03:44:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have this problem as well, would be very interested in a fix.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-20T06:25:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222637621\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142020\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466369722\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022He_162\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 hours ago, He_162 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere is a GIF showing the rippling in slower motion, just like 7 screenshots, but it shows that it happens.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/oKhoXIY\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://imgur.com/oKhoXIY\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027re using time warp and the shadow is moving because of the rotation of Kerbin. You say this is slow motion. Can you explain what you mean?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Majorjim!","CreatedById":61954,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-20T06:25:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222637784\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142020\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466377718\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u00222511\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Corona688\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, Corona688 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEh, I\u0027ve noticed that in every game which has shadows for as long as I\u0027ve known to look for it.\u00A0 Unless you pump shadows up to a ludicrously high res, I don\u0027t think it\u0027s really avoidable.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have not.\u00A0 It was not present in KSP before the move to unity 5 either.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222637931\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142020\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466388011\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152460\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022swjr-swis\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, swjr-swis said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTwo short videos showing the problem:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI cannot view those.. Do you have a YT account?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222638123\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142020\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466403938\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002262955\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Deddly\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Deddly said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027re using time warp and the shadow is moving because of the rotation of Kerbin. You say this is slow motion. Can you explain what you mean?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe bug looks like a rippling effect, imagine the shadow at the edges has slices taken out of it. It moves quick even at normal time step.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-20T06:31:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222638124\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142020\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466403941\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002261954\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Majorjim\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, Majorjim said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe bug looks like a rippling effect, imagine the shadow at the edges has slices taken out of it. It moves quick even at normal time step.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have seen that in previous versions when changing the settings for shadow detail. I haven\u0027t fiddled with those setting in the latest version though. But all I see in \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/152811-he_162/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022152811\u0022 href=\u0022%7B___base_url___%7D/index.php?/profile/152811-he_162/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@He_162\u003C/a\u003E\u0027s first .gif is a short timelapse of a moving shadow.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Majorjim!","CreatedById":61954,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-20T06:32:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 